imdb.plot outline: Haunting History is a paranormal web series that digs into the history of the locations being investigated by the Four State Paranormal team. After a thorough search into the past, the team then seeks to find answers as to whether or not a location is haunted.
imdb.title: Haunting History
plot: _Haunting History_ (qv) is a paranormal web series that digs into the history of the locations being investigated by the Four State Paranormal team. After a thorough search into the past, the team then seeks to find answers as to whether or not a location is haunted.
